message.content:
1. A log-rank test was used to compare survival curves.
2. The comparison was between dihydroartemisinin-piperaquine and chloroquine.
3. The log-rank test confirmed the superiority of dihydroartemisinin-piperaquine over chloroquine.
4. The p-value of the test was 0.003.
